   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>Go to <menucascade>
                  <uicontrol>Setup </uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol> Build </uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol> Develop </uicontrol>
                  <uicontrol> Custom Settings</uicontrol>
               </menucascade> and click <uicontrol>Manage</uicontrol> next to
                  <uicontrol>Power-Adobe</uicontrol> Settings. </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click the <uicontrol>Edit</uicontrol> button.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Select the <uicontrol>Don't Copy Opportunity</uicontrol> to disallow all User/profiles from copying the Agreement record to the Opportunity.</p>
            <p>
               <note type="tip" id="note_jd1_1fk_rcc">
                  <p>Configuring the Power-Adobe Custom Settings will override the Admin setting.
                     For the Admin settings to work, the Power-Adobe Settings cannot have any values
                     in them (this includes the Default Organization Level). </p>
               </note>
            </p>
         </li>
      </ol>
